      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You know how to find people who are always looking for stolen animals & vehicles, whether to provide for animal pit fights, or to supply some desperate rogues the means to get away faster on mounts during an illegal job. This contact not only provides you with information of what such animals & vehicles are in high demand in the area, but also offers to give you favors and information (DM choice) if you bring such animals & vehicles to them."
          }
        ]
      },
